Degenerus","details":"This module is called via `delegatecall` from DegenerusGame during state 1 (setup),      meaning all storage reads/writes operate on the game contract's storage. ## When Called After a level ends (via extermination or timeout), the game transitions to state 1 and calls `finalizeEndgame()` to settle payouts before starting the next level. ## Settlement Flow ``` finalizeEndgame()     |     +- IF extermination occurred (not timeout):     |   +- Mint exterminator trophy (winnings packed)     |   +- Pay exterminator (20-40% of prize pool)     |   |   +- 25% of their share \u2192 bonds (if enabled)     |   +- Pay extermination jackpot (trait ticket holders)     |   +- Pay purchase rewards (20% \u2192 NFT/MAP rewards for winners)     |     +- IF previous level > 0:         +- Mint affiliate trophy for top affiliate         +- Run reward jackpots:             +- BAF (every 10 levels): 10-25% of rewardPool             +- Decimator (levels 15,25,35...85): 15% of rewardPool ``` ## Exterminator Share Calculation - \"Big-ex\" levels (14, 24, 34...): Fixed 40% - All other levels: Random 20-40% (VRF-derived, 1% steps) ## Bond Integration Several payout paths route a portion to bonds: - Exterminator: 25% of their share \u2192 bonds - BAF top winners: 20% \u2192 bonds - BAF scatter winners: remainder after MAPs \u2192 bonds (100%) This finalizeEndgame(uint24,uint256,address,a.details: Called via delegatecall from DegenerusGame during state 1.

params.coinContract: BURNIE coin contract for reward credits.
params.jackpotModuleAddr: Address of jackpot module for delegatecall.
params.lvl: Current level index (1-based) - this is the NEW level after advancement.
params.nftAddr: NFT contract for queuing reward mints. ## State Changes - `currentPrizePool`  0 (after extermination settlement) - `claimablePool` += all ETH payouts - `nextPrizePool` += purchase reward pool (funds next level) - `rewardPool` -= BAF/Decimator jackpot spends - `bondPool` += bond deposits from split payouts - `airdropIndex`  0 (reset for next level) ## Extermination vs Timeout - Extermination: `lastExterminatedTrait != 420` - full settlement with payouts - Timeout: `lastExterminatedTrait == 420` - skip exterminator/jackpot payouts
params.rngWord: VRF entropy for jackpot selection and randomization.

finalizeEndgame(uint24,uint256,address,a.notice: Settle a completed level by paying exterminator, jackpots, and rewards.
